---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Privacy Policy for Sheepdog Cyber Defense LLC.">
  <section>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">Last updated: February 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>Sheepdog Cyber Defense LLC ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website https://sheepdogcyberdefense.com.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Through our contact form, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name</li>
      <li>Company (if provided)</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>City/Area (optional)</li>
      <li>Service interest (optional)</li>
      <li>Message content</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We also collect the submission timestamp and basic technical information (IP address, user agent) that Netlify Forms provides.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to your inquiry</li>
      <li>Provide quotes or information about our services</li>
      <li>Communicate with you about ongoing engagements</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain contact form submissions for our business records. We do not set an automatic expiration but will honor deletion requests where feasible.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. The only third party involved is Netlify, Inc., our hosting provider, which processes form submissions on our behalf.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no method of electronic transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us at sheepdogcyberdefense@protonmail.com.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Contact us at: sheepdogcyberdefense@protonmail.com</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
</style>
